4... Qh4 { Your e pawn is hanging! Defend it } 5. Nc3 Bb4 { It's time for a sacrifice! Be2 is the move here, sacrificing the e4 pawn. } 6. Be2 Qxe4 { Now, Nb5 threatens a fork on c7. } 7. Nb5 Bxc3+ { Don't do anything crazy lol! } 8. bxc3 { Now Kd8 is to prevent getting forked on c7.
